Information about album:
Paul Williams 1971 album Just An Old Fashioned Love Song, plus 1998 self titled compilation album and a couple of another popular track.
Notable songs, that were hits for other artists, on the Old Fashioned Love Song album include "(Just An) Old Fashioned Love Song", "We've Only Just Begun", "Let Me Be the One" and "When I Was All Alone", while Evergreen was a big hit for Barbra Streisand
